509
00:25:27,592 --> 00:25:29,651
Lice! Oh, my God!

510
00:25:29,794 --> 00:25:31,591
I couldn't get out
of there fast enough.

511
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:34,164
I just kept picturing
little tiny bugs

512
00:25:34,299 --> 00:25:37,200
