00:27:35,954 --> 00:27:37,421
Yep, I'll be there.

556
00:27:37,555 --> 00:27:38,920
OK. Ow!

557
00:27:39,057 --> 00:27:40,615
OK, bye-bye. Bye.

558
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:44,628
