580
00:28:51,529 --> 00:28:54,191
Iong days, late nights,
and I just wanna make sure

581
00:28:54,332 --> 00:28:56,630
it won't be too much for you,
considering what you're up against

582
00:28:56,768 --> 00:28:58,030
with the six kids and the lice.

583
00:28:58,737 --> 00:29:00,762
Oh, my... Oh, my God!

584
00:29:01,806 --> 00:29:04,468
- How do you know...?
- Your text message was showing.

585
00:29:04,609 --> 00:29:07,305
- I can read upside down.
- [laughs] Oh.

586
00:29:07,445 --> 00:29:10,972
So... what do you think, Kate?

587
00:29:11,783 --> 00:29:13,250
Can you swing it?

