664
00:32:20,305 --> 00:32:21,499
We didn't know what tofu was.

665
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,932
Oh, but that was a simpler time.

666
00:32:24,075 --> 00:32:26,407
And everybody knew their place,
what they had to do.

667
00:32:26,544 --> 00:32:29,604
Lew made the money,
I changed the diapers,

668
00:32:29,747 --> 00:32:32,215
if we couldn't pay the bills,
that was Lew's fault.

669
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:35,808
The kids were crying,
that was me.

670
00:32:35,954 --> 00:32:37,421
But boy, you all...

671
00:32:37,555 --> 00:32:40,991
If something goes wrong,
it's everybody's fault.

672
00:32:41,125 --> 00:32:43,491
I don't think that does
anyone any good.

673
00:32:43,628 --> 00:32:46,961
Well, I think it's...
I think it's just a more complicated...

674
00:32:47,098 --> 00:32:49,794
Well, it's as complicated
as you make it, dear.

675
00:32:50,902 --> 00:32:52,631
You know, I was wondering,

676
00:32:52,770 --> 00:32:54,601
if you had stayed home with Ben,

677
00:32:54,739 --> 00:32:56,536
