which isn't as comforting, actually.

697
00:33:57,068 --> 00:33:59,127
[sighs]

698
00:34:08,212 --> 00:34:10,112
What's this?
What are you doing?

699
00:34:10,848 --> 00:34:12,338
Hm?

700
00:34:12,483 --> 00:34:14,383
